WEBVTT

00:00:00.749 --> 00:00:03.157
-erman film numer tsvey.

00:00:03.753 --> 00:00:05.924
mir hobn gehaltn in redn

00:00:06.470 --> 00:00:08.979
vegn ayere shkheynim,

00:00:09.187 --> 00:00:13.164
un ir hot gezogt az in shtub hot gevoynt mit aykh der zeyde,

00:00:13.557 --> 00:00:17.804
zogt mir di bobes dermont mir ayere bobes.

00:00:19.359 --> 00:00:21.567
di bobe iz geshtorbn

00:00:23.007 --> 00:00:29.077
a lange tsayt frier, az ikh ge- ikh hob nisht gedenkt, ikh gede- yetst avade nisht gedenk ikh dokh nisht tsu fil.

00:00:29.335 --> 00:00:30.579
vi hot zi geheysn?

00:00:30.820 --> 00:00:32.030
Khane Baylik

00:00:33.453 --> 00:00:36.873
un der andere bobe gedenk ikh nisht oyfn itstikn ⟨minut⟩ UNK

00:00:37.132 --> 00:00:39.067
oykhet geven, iz geven geshtorbn.

00:00:41.722 --> 00:00:45.310
vi azoy iz geven dos religyeze lebn fun dayn mishpokhe?

00:00:46.008 --> 00:00:49.659
bay undz in shtetl iz nisht bloyz di mishpokhe

00:00:49.659 --> 00:00:52.735
dos gatnse shtub iz geven zeyer zeyer religyez,

00:00:53.214 --> 00:00:57.849
AND yedn in der fri ze'mir gegnagen in shul arayn davenun in der fri,

00:00:58.175 --> 00:01:02.422
un nakher bay der nakht ze'mir gegangen davenen minkhe mayrev.

00:01:02.782 --> 00:01:06.370
dos gantse shtetl yidn, ale geven religyez.

00:01:06.899 --> 00:01:09.830
un se gekumen fraytik nokh mitog

00:01:10.072 --> 00:01:12.732
hot men zikh shoyn tsugegreyt far shabes,

00:01:12.873 --> 00:01:17.930
vayl shabes hot men gehaltn iz a mitsve tsu hobn, optsuesn a gutn

00:01:18.256 --> 00:01:21.946
esn bay der nakht, optsurikhtn

00:01:22.323 --> 00:01:24.612
di ka- dos tsu makhn kidesh,

00:01:24.888 --> 00:01:32.409
AND oyb eyner in undzer shtetl, se dort geven efsher a tsvey azelkhe familyes, zey zenen geven zeyer orem, ⟨mit⟩ a sakh kinder,

00:01:32.583 --> 00:01:35.935
az er hot nisht gehat tsu tsu koyfn oyf shabes

00:01:36.110 --> 00:01:40.340
ze'mir arumgegangen undz hobn tsuzamgenumen, nisht gezogt far vemener,

00:01:40.649 --> 00:01:42.882
un me hot zey geholfn az zoln hobn

00:01:42.882 --> 00:01:44.477
se geven vi a mitsve

00:01:44.477 --> 00:01:47.039
tsu esn tsuzamen mit di familye,

00:01:47.197 --> 00:01:50.397
far fraytik bay der nakht un tsu makhn kidesh.

00:01:51.061 --> 00:01:55.595
un yede fraytik UNK hot gehat a beker in shtetl a yidishn

00:01:55.752 --> 00:01:57.890
hobn di familyes gemakht tsholnt

00:01:58.233 --> 00:02:03.560
vayl me hot dokh nisht getort kokhn, keyner i- in SNIELOW vet nisht kokhn shabes

00:02:03.819 --> 00:02:06.429
me hot afiles keyn shteyn nisht oyfgehoybn um shabes,

00:02:06.670 --> 00:02:09.165
hot men gemakht di familyes tsholnt,

00:02:09.168 --> 00:02:12.909
un me hot es ahingetrogn tsu dem beker, er iz geshtanen bay im iber nakht,

00:02:13.488 --> 00:02:16.317
un meiz gegangen davenen ye- shabes in der fri

00:02:16.711 --> 00:02:19.827
un nokhn davenen ze'mir geganen aroysnemen dos tsholnt

00:02:20.069 --> 00:02:23.877
un me hot gegesn, kimat dos gantse shtetl azoy gefirt zikh,

00:02:24.237 --> 00:02:26.274
un shoyn. nakher nokhn esn

00:02:26.380 --> 00:02:31.339
eltere mentshn hobn zikh gevolt ⟨tsuleygn⟩ hobn zikh tsugeleygt in der heym, yingere zey hobn gevolt zenen gegangen in vald arayn,

00:02:31.339 --> 00:02:33.597
opruen zikh fun di gantse vokh,

00:02:33.856 --> 00:02:37.360
shabes, nakher me iz aheymgekkumen hot men shoyn gegesn mikhiks,

00:02:37.501 --> 00:02:42.828
se iz shoyn adurkh zeks sho, vayl me vet nisht esn milkh, bald milkhiks mit fleyshik,

00:02:42.901 --> 00:02:46.189
me hot, dos gantse shtetl me hot zeyer ongehitn dos yidishkeyt.

00:02:46.209 --> 00:02:49.207
se geven kimat ale yidn hobn gehat berd,

00:02:49.769 --> 00:02:53.825
hobn undz gehat di di yidishe hitlekh,

00:02:53.825 --> 00:02:57.256
sepetsyel, mit azelkhe kapotes,

00:02:57.785 --> 00:03:00.524
un se geven SOME FAMILIES hobn nisht

00:03:00.524 --> 00:03:02.313
ikh hob nisht gehat keyn peyes,

00:03:02.358 --> 00:03:06.369
ikh hob ge- zeyer ongehitn dos yidishkeyt, ikh bin gevezn

00:03:06.509 --> 00:03:09.406
gedavnt dray mol a tog,

00:03:09.648 --> 00:03:14.401
und ikh bin gegangen a halbn tog tog in der fri in di poylishe shule,

00:03:14.508 --> 00:03:18.333
ikh hob zikh zeyer gut gelernt un ikh hob gele- geglikhn zikh tsu lernen,

00:03:18.474 --> 00:03:21.252
un a halbn tog bin ikh geganen in kheyder arayn,

00:03:21.933 --> 00:03:27.237
und s- me iz geven ale tsufridn. un yede got hot men zikh gezen mit di khaveyrim,

00:03:27.265 --> 00:03:30.351
dos shtetl iz geven kleyn, vi me iz aroys hot men zikh getrofn,

00:03:30.370 --> 00:03:32.727
me iz gegangen in shtub arayn eyner tsun andern,

00:03:33.155 --> 00:03:36.524
ir zent geven onhengers fun a a rov?

00:03:36.648 --> 00:03:37.469
un a rebn?

00:03:38.032 --> 00:03:42.380
dos gantse shtetl hot gehert tsu dem rov. se geven eyn rov un dos gatnse shtetl hot gehert tsu dem rov.

00:03:40.972 --> 00:03:43.766
vi hot er geheysn gedenkt ir?

00:03:42.841 --> 00:03:47.645
ikh veys nisht, gedenk nisht, er hot gehat eyn zun hot er gehat der rov gedenk ikh, ye

00:03:48.089 --> 00:03:49.569
un dan iz geven a rebe,

00:03:49.726 --> 00:03:54.094
der rebe iz ge- me hot im gerufn der Tarler rebe. se do a shtetl

00:03:54.130 --> 00:03:56.302
nisht vayt hot es geheysn Tarlo,

00:03:57.657 --> 00:04:00.132
T. A. R. L. O.

00:04:01.117 --> 00:04:02.410
W. MAYBE,

00:04:02.619 --> 00:04:04.874
un er iz geven zeyer a bakanter rebe

00:04:06.567 --> 00:04:11.928
un a helft shtetl iz geganen tsu dem rebn davenen, a halb shtetl do mitn rov hot men gedavnt.

00:04:12.085 --> 00:04:14.999
un eyn mol hob ikh gezeen vi a yid

00:04:15.258 --> 00:04:18.442
hot zikh geshtelt a hoyz punkt antkegn fun di shul,

00:04:18.920 --> 00:04:22.863
AND di goyim hobn arbet, dos UNK es shabes,

00:04:22.953 --> 00:04:27.025
iz der rov gekumen davenen in shul arayn shabes, hot er gezeen, shabes!

00:04:27.070 --> 00:04:30.828
se far a yidishn balbos arbetn, iz me tor nisht arbetn!

00:04:31.441 --> 00:04:37.156
un un me hot es ongeshtelt. er hot aroyfgerufn dem manen vos me hot geshtelt far im dos hoyz

00:04:37.263 --> 00:04:39.699
un me hot oyfgehert tsu arbetn shabes.

00:04:39.699 --> 00:04:41.999
zeyer ongehitn dos yidishkeyt dort.

00:04:41.684 --> 00:04:47.129
zogt mir, ir dermont ayer, di andere yontoyvim vos me hot gepravet bay aykh?

00:04:47.641 --> 00:04:49.441
tsum batshpil peysekh?

00:04:48.215 --> 00:04:51.500
SURE! rosheshone, yomkiper,

00:04:51.607 --> 00:04:55.972
shvues, sukes. sukes hot men yeder eyner gemakht a suke,

00:04:56.146 --> 00:04:57.493
AND

00:04:57.493 --> 00:05:01.240
shvues me hot kez-kukhn gebakn, se geven a

00:05:01.240 --> 00:05:03.003
a yontev iz gekumen

00:05:03.031 --> 00:05:04.747
iz geven a yontev.

00:05:05.377 --> 00:05:06.957
es benkt zikh nokh dem!

00:05:07.435 --> 00:05:10.906
dertseylt mir, vi hot ir gepravet peysekh tsum bayshpil?

00:05:11.637 --> 00:05:17.321
peysekh hot men gepravet in di shtub. yeder eyner me hot zikh gebarimt di kinder

00:05:17.358 --> 00:05:21.757
az bay undz hot men shpeter hot men zezitsn barn seyder vos shpeter,

00:05:22.049 --> 00:05:26.026
un ongerikht dem seyder azoy biz tsvelef bay der nakht, eynser bay der nakht.

00:05:26.369 --> 00:05:28.304
un nisht gegesn keyn khomets,

00:05:28.360 --> 00:05:32.337
yede hot zikh gekoyft naye antseger oyf peysekh, naye shikh,

00:05:32.495 --> 00:05:36.860
oyb eyner hot zikh nisht gekoyft hot men oysgereynikt di tashn fun di krishelekh,

00:05:37.017 --> 00:05:40.724
i- me zol nisht onrirn keyn khomets. zeyer zeyer opgehitn.

00:05:40.797 --> 00:05:41.461
zeyer!

00:05:41.461 --> 00:05:44.437
se geven, gants Poyln iz geven religyez,

00:05:44.577 --> 00:05:45.537
mit di yidn.

00:05:45.537 --> 00:05:48.942
se hot zikh getrofn efsher in di groyse shtet vos ikh hob nisht gezeen

00:05:49.167 --> 00:05:53.195
veyls ikh nisht, BUT, SNIELOW iz geven zeyer religyez dos gantse shtetl.

00:05:53.184 --> 00:05:56.384
ver hot ongefirt mitn seyder bay aykh in shtub?

00:05:56.491 --> 00:05:57.650
⟨in⟩ der zeyde.

00:05:57.976 --> 00:05:58.662
ye

00:05:59.529 --> 00:06:00.232
m

00:06:01.081 --> 00:06:02.442
der zeyde vos hot ge-

00:06:01.250 --> 00:06:03.168
ye vi iz geven a seyder?

00:06:03.832 --> 00:06:05.800
me hot zikh frier tsugeleygt,

00:06:06.329 --> 00:06:08.028
un di mame hot gekokht,

00:06:08.118 --> 00:06:11.994
di ale zakhn far fish, mit di ale zakhn

00:06:12.084 --> 00:06:16.347
un mit dem gantsn, vos me darf, dos bitern mit do mit UNK,

00:06:16.420 --> 00:06:20.434
un shoyn, nakher yetst gekumen, me hot arayngelozt oyfgemakht di tir,

00:06:20.470 --> 00:06:24.245
Eliyohu Hanovi zol araynkumen. me hot aleyn gemakht dem vayn oykhet,

00:06:24.790 --> 00:06:25.513
ye

00:06:25.550 --> 00:06:29.268
un den in shtetl hot men gebakn matses far peysekh,

00:06:29.296 --> 00:06:31.484
iz geven eyner vos hot gehat a

00:06:32.215 --> 00:06:33.386
a bekeray,

00:06:33.386 --> 00:06:38.102
hot zi kosher gemakht di gantse bekeray un di froyen fun shtetl

00:06:38.139 --> 00:06:41.322
a sakh ahingegangen helfn dort un me hot gevelgert

00:06:41.429 --> 00:06:45.052
un gebakn di matses oyf peysekh dort in di bekeray.

00:06:46.205 --> 00:06:49.287
ir dermant zikh vi men hot tsugegreyt dos vayn?

00:06:49.917 --> 00:06:55.109
fun rozhinkes. oysgekvetshte rozhinkes a- az- azoy fun rozhinkes

00:06:55.250 --> 00:06:55.936
ye

00:06:56.077 --> 00:06:59.649
dertseylt mir vi azoy iz geven rosheshone oder yomkiper

00:07:00.025 --> 00:07:01.437
rosheshone

00:07:02.455 --> 00:07:04.587
roshe- yomkiper gedenk ikh

00:07:04.632 --> 00:07:06.697
vayl ikh hob es nisht lib gehat azoy

00:07:06.708 --> 00:07:09.571
vayl ale froyen zenen gekumen tsun shul

00:07:09.644 --> 00:07:11.596
un zey hobn geveynt a sakh

00:07:13.694 --> 00:07:16.608
zey hobn vi me mishpet a

00:07:17.170 --> 00:07:19.882
hobn zey hobn moyre gehat, veyst, far got,

00:07:19.972 --> 00:07:23.139
hobn zey geveynt a sakh un UNK a kind

00:07:23.313 --> 00:07:27.948
hob ikh nisht geglikhn yomkiper. me hot ongetsundn di likh in di shul,

00:07:28.460 --> 00:07:33.618
un me hot gehat a goy hot akht gegebn, se nisht geven azoy ELECTRICITY vi in Amerike oder do,

00:07:33.894 --> 00:07:37.837
hot men gemuzt akhtsun gebn se zol nisht makhn keyn fayer fun di likht,

00:07:38.619 --> 00:07:42.089
un un me hot gefast. yeder eyner hot gefast, nisht gegesn.

00:07:42.618 --> 00:07:43.861
dos iz geven yomkiper.

00:07:43.192 --> 00:07:45.211
es iz geven a shabes goy?

00:07:46.212 --> 00:07:51.719
ye, me hot shtendik gehat a shabes goy er zol akhtung gebn, oystsuleshn oyb me darf epes tuen,

00:07:51.730 --> 00:07:53.559
vos a yid tor nisht tuen

00:07:53.587 --> 00:07:55.387
fun di religye zayt,

00:07:55.629 --> 00:07:58.795
iz geven a shabes goy, hot er akht gegebn shtendik.

00:07:58.919 --> 00:07:59.572
ye

00:07:59.611 --> 00:08:03.824
ir dermont zikh an andern yontev, an ander gelegnheyt?

00:08:03.880 --> 00:08:06.710
ikh ⟨hob geredt vegn⟩ shvues, me hot gebakn

00:08:07.776 --> 00:08:10.442
kez-kukhlekh, ales fun kez,

00:08:10.462 --> 00:08:11.654
se geven sheyn.

00:08:11.727 --> 00:08:13.991
purim hot ir geba- hot gefayert?

00:08:13.533 --> 00:08:16.078
purim? ye oykhet, purim,

00:08:16.078 --> 00:08:18.505
me iz geganen in shul mit di kofes,

00:08:18.714 --> 00:08:24.699
un khaneke hot undz di eltern, der zeyde gegebn a por groshn, vifl me hot gekent,

00:08:25.244 --> 00:08:28.141
un me hot me iz geven tsufridn.

00:08:28.231 --> 00:08:29.710
me iz geven tsugevoynt

00:08:29.784 --> 00:08:34.182
fun dem lebn fun dem shtetl, me hot nisht gevust fun keyn besers,

00:08:34.323 --> 00:08:38.671
un dos iz geven i- di beste zakh iz geven, di FAMILIES zenen geven tsuzamen.

00:08:39.200 --> 00:08:41.725
a tate, a mame, a mume, a feter,

00:08:41.815 --> 00:08:43.447
vos haynt hot men es nisht.

00:08:43.840 --> 00:08:47.716
ir hot zikh farzamlt oyf di yontoyvim di gantse mishpokhe?

00:08:47.485 --> 00:08:48.678
yeder tog.

00:08:48.768 --> 00:08:50.129
yeder tog.

00:08:50.337 --> 00:08:52.357
yede tog, me hot gevoynt derlebn.

00:08:52.801 --> 00:08:55.732
se nisht geven keyn tog me zol zikh nisht zen eyner mitn andern.

00:08:56.142 --> 00:08:57.115
yede tog

00:08:57.037 --> 00:08:59.849
un vifl mentshn zaynen gezesn baym tish?

00:09:00.175 --> 00:09:03.376
peysekh tsum bayshpil, oder rosheshone?

00:09:03.500 --> 00:09:05.097
se geven, di gantse FAMILY.

00:09:05.154 --> 00:09:06.855
di FAMILY, nisht di

00:09:06.855 --> 00:09:08.433
lomir zogn ikh hob gehat an onkl,

00:09:08.433 --> 00:09:11.023
der onkl hot zikh ⟨ongerikht⟩ dem seyder mit zayn FAMILY,

00:09:11.023 --> 00:09:13.133
undz hobn gemakht mit undzer FAMILY,

00:09:13.133 --> 00:09:16.153
me iz nisht gegangen eyn FAMILY, vi in Amerike makht men

00:09:16.153 --> 00:09:17.816
me farbet di andere,

00:09:17.827 --> 00:09:21.550
dort di FAMILIES hobn zikh ⟨opgerikht⟩ far zikh.

00:09:22.265 --> 00:09:27.254
ir hot frier ongehoybn tsu dertseyln vegn der shule un vegn dem kheyder

00:09:27.277 --> 00:09:28.047
ye

00:09:27.800 --> 00:09:31.270
yo, dertseylt mir. ven hot ir ongehoybn tsu lernen in kheyder?

00:09:33.234 --> 00:09:34.645
azoy vi

00:09:35.056 --> 00:09:36.282
⟨AS A⟩ kind.

00:09:36.710 --> 00:09:39.762
ikh gedenk nisht vifl yor, me hot mikh bald genumen in kheyder arayn tsu lernen,

00:09:39.762 --> 00:09:41.649
koydem me hot dokh gemuzt kenen di davenen,

00:09:41.890 --> 00:09:44.197
hot men dokh gemuzt oyslernen zikh davenen,

00:09:44.725 --> 00:09:48.432
un nakher in di andere shule, in di poylishe,

00:09:48.624 --> 00:09:52.820
gedenk ikh iz geven bay a zeks yor hot men shoyn ongehoybn tsu geyn in shule arayn,

00:09:52.927 --> 00:09:54.355
gloyb ikh bay zeks.

00:09:54.682 --> 00:09:56.094
un in der heym

00:09:56.217 --> 00:09:59.519
az eyner, ESPECIALLY in di groyse shtet

00:09:59.778 --> 00:10:04.835
iz geven yidn vos hobn geredt poylish. in undzer shtetl az eyner hot geredt poylish

00:10:04.925 --> 00:10:08.649
hot men gekukt oyf im azoy vi er volt nisht geven keyn opgehitener yid.

00:10:09.093 --> 00:10:12.327
hot men gelernt kinder di ershte zakh yidish,

00:10:12.485 --> 00:10:15.570
un di eltern hobn gezogt ven me vet geyn in di poylishe shule

00:10:15.607 --> 00:10:18.588
vet men zikh shoyn oyslernen poylish un azoy iz es geven.

00:10:18.796 --> 00:10:22.098
ikh hob zikh gut gelernt in di poylishe shule oykhet.

00:10:22.812 --> 00:10:25.557
bashraybt mir vi azoy iz geven der kheyder

00:10:26.170 --> 00:10:29.135
der kheyder, se geven, koydem iz geven a melamed.

00:10:29.849 --> 00:10:31.480
un er hot gehat kinder,

00:10:31.672 --> 00:10:35.902
vos di eltern hobn getsolt, ikh veys nisht vifl yede vokh.

00:10:36.549 --> 00:10:38.635
azoy hot er zikh

00:10:38.709 --> 00:10:40.289
gemakht a lebn derfun.

00:10:40.548 --> 00:10:46.499
un me iz gegangen yede tog in kheyder arayn. er hot undz gelernt koydem tsu davenen,

00:10:46.623 --> 00:10:48.307
un tsu laynen

00:10:48.310 --> 00:10:50.094
nakher tsum shraybn,

00:10:50.319 --> 00:10:54.290
un in di krig hot men dokh nisht farbotn,

00:10:54.290 --> 00:10:58.987
ye, in di poylishe hot men dokh gehat do a halbe tog un di poylishe shule a halbe tog,

00:10:59.144 --> 00:11:01.243
un me iz aheymgekumen, me hot zikh gelernt,

00:11:01.254 --> 00:11:02.463
HOMEWORK,

00:11:03.144 --> 00:11:05.056
ober in di krig

00:11:05.056 --> 00:11:09.213
azoy vi di doytshn zenen arayn hot men farbotn yidishe kinder tsu geyn in shule arayn.

00:11:09.877 --> 00:11:11.086
shoyn nisht gekent geyn.

00:11:11.412 --> 00:11:13.358
hobn di eltern fun di yidn

00:11:13.358 --> 00:11:14.647
gefunen

00:11:14.720 --> 00:11:15.746
TUTORS

00:11:15.746 --> 00:11:18.730
TUTORS vos er vil lernen privat

00:11:18.837 --> 00:11:20.755
un dos hot men nisht getort

00:11:20.829 --> 00:11:24.130
BUT me hot gevolt oyslernen di kinder,

00:11:24.220 --> 00:11:25.390
ze'mir

00:11:25.390 --> 00:11:28.079
hob ikh gehat azoyne, zi hot mikh gelernt di poylishe,

00:11:28.203 --> 00:11:30.391
un di yidn hobn gemakht

00:11:30.717 --> 00:11:32.942
vi a yeshive mit dray

00:11:32.962 --> 00:11:33.969
klasn

00:11:34.582 --> 00:11:38.156
un ikh hob, mikh hot men shoyn demolts gelernt gemore,

00:11:38.159 --> 00:11:39.470
Bobe Metsie,

00:11:40.252 --> 00:11:41.596
un

