UNK zogt eyner UNK er heyst Firer,

00:23:10.310 --> 00:23:12.560
gib undz milkhome, me vet zikh shlogn,

00:23:12.785 --> 00:23:14.905
un Hitler hot nisht nokhgegebn,

00:23:15.080 --> 00:23:17.302
me hot shoyn gezen az se kumt a milkhome.

00:23:17.425 --> 00:23:17.817
UNK

00:23:17.594 --> 00:23:19.718
BUT di eltern hobn geredt

00:23:19.718 --> 00:23:21.655
me hot dokh moyre gehat far di doytshn

00:23:22.100 --> 00:23:25.092
hot men gezogt az di doytshn in di

00:23:25.092 --> 00:23:28.321
ershte velts-milkhome zenen nisht geven azoy shlekht tsu yidn,

00:23:28.377 --> 00:23:30.515
me hot zikh nisht forgeshtelt vos kumt.

00:23:31.060 --> 00:23:31.662
ye

00:23:31.415 --> 00:23:33.856
vi alt zent ir geven in der moment?

00:23:34.300 --> 00:23:35.628
a fertsn yor.

00:23:39.430 --> 00:23:41.807
men hot geredt bay aykh in shtub

00:23:41.807 --> 00:23:43.374
vegn avekforn?

00:23:44.206 --> 00:23:44.960
NO

00:23:45.269 --> 00:23:47.457
NO. me hot zikh nisht forgeshtelt azlekhe zakhn.

00:23:52.627 --> 00:23:57.042
biz der moment hot ir epes gehert vegn di natsis?

00:23:59.931 --> 00:24:00.673
YES.

00:24:00.673 --> 00:24:01.345
YEA.

00:24:01.419 --> 00:24:05.379
vayl se iz ongekumen keyn Tshmerlev iz ongekumen a sakh pleytim.

00:24:05.722 --> 00:24:07.077
nu pleytim vos iz.

00:24:07.105 --> 00:24:12.820
vos Hitler hot zey aroysgefirt, ershtns hot er aroysgefirt di vos zenen geboyrn in Poyln un zey hobn gevoynt in Doytshland.

00:24:13.164 --> 00:24:16.938
un di a sakh fun zey gekumen keyn Tshmerlev oykhet,

00:24:17.079 --> 00:24:20.364
un di kehile, di Tshmerlever dos hot geshafn

00:24:20.757 --> 00:24:28.042
a kikh far zey un me zol zey gebn esn und a voynung, ⟨iz⟩ a sakh hobn gevoynt in shul, zey hobn nisht gehat vu tsu geyn,

00:24:28.419 --> 00:24:32.598
me hot shoyn gezeen di zakhn, ye, me hot shoyn gezen az,

00:24:32.840 --> 00:24:35.720
ober me hot zikh ales nisht forgeshtelt vos se vet kumen.

00:24:38.898 --> 00:24:40.347
dertseylt mir

00:24:40.347 --> 00:24:42.774
ven iz oysgebrokhn di milkhome.

00:24:43.640 --> 00:24:46.342
di ershte moment vos iz geshen?

00:24:44.990 --> 00:24:46.419
di ershte moment

00:24:46.576 --> 00:24:48.168
iz hobn zey

00:24:48.213 --> 00:24:50.384
zey hobn undz gelernt

00:24:50.542 --> 00:24:51.340
a vokh

00:24:51.340 --> 00:24:53.455
far di milkhome, di radyos,

00:24:53.512 --> 00:24:55.120
az Doytshland

00:24:55.939 --> 00:24:58.282
varft a sakh POISON,

00:24:58.625 --> 00:25:00.174
sam, arunter.

00:25:00.177 --> 00:25:03.699
se kukt oys vi poylishe CHokolad, me zol nisht oyfheybn.

00:25:03.772 --> 00:25:05.285
vayl dos iz sam.

00:25:05.459 --> 00:25:09.740
un un me zol akhtung gebn, me zol akhtung gebn oyf shpyonen,

00:25:09.999 --> 00:25:12.507
doytshe shpyonen tsi zey geyen nisht.

00:25:12.682 --> 00:25:14.046
un un shoyn.

00:25:14.049 --> 00:25:17.235
nakher nayntsn nayn un draysik, dos gedenk ikh,

00:25:17.238 --> 00:25:22.838
se hot oysgebrokhn di milkhome, iz gekumen, ye, un az me vet varfn gaz, hobn zey gezogt,

00:25:22.874 --> 00:25:24.708
hobn undz geleygt, undz hobn genumen vate,

00:25:24.882 --> 00:25:27.419
⟨aynnetsn⟩ in in vaser,

00:25:27.447 --> 00:25:30.566
arayngeyn shtub, tsumahn di shtubn gut, di fentster,

00:25:30.566 --> 00:25:33.044
un zikh tsuleygn tsu di noz

00:25:33.219 --> 00:25:34.850
me zol zikh nisht opgazn.

00:25:35.176 --> 00:25:41.063
gedenk ikh eyn mol iz gekumen a a, ven di krig hot oysgeborkhn hot a AIRPLANE aropgevorfn a bombe

00:25:41.099 --> 00:25:42.595
se gefaln

00:25:42.955 --> 00:25:46.277
oyf di gaz rern, me hot shoyn gehat demolts in Tshmerlev UNK

00:25:46.277 --> 00:25:46.918
un se hot

00:25:46.918 --> 00:25:48.350
aroys a fayer,

00:25:48.423 --> 00:25:51.219
hobn zey ongehoybn tsu zogn, "oh! gevorfn gaz!"

00:25:52.085 --> 00:25:58.132
hohn undz gehat a ge-, dos gesheft, fun UNK me hot gehat vate, hot ver se iz adurkhgeganen hot men arayngerufn in gesheft arayn

00:25:58.143 --> 00:26:01.726
kum arayn, me hot tsurisn di vate, me hot zey tsugeleygt tsu di noz

00:26:01.754 --> 00:26:05.455
un eyner hot zikh epes shir farkhalesht, er hot gemeynt az er hot, er hot shoyn di gaz,

00:26:05.455 --> 00:26:06.946
se nisht geven keyn gaz.

00:26:07.222 --> 00:26:10.574
un, ibergeshrokn, zeyer moyre gehat far di bombes.

00:26:11.154 --> 00:26:16.669
un nu shoyn. un nakher yede tog hot men gebombardirt un ikh hob zeyer ale

00:26:16.705 --> 00:26:19.569
zeyer zeyer moyre gehat far di bombes, varfn.

00:26:19.895 --> 00:26:23.163
un me iz shoyn nisht geshlofn, undz hobn gevoynt fornt

00:26:23.270 --> 00:26:25.596
hot moyre gehat tsu shlofn, di doytshn veln araynkumen

00:26:25.596 --> 00:26:27.460
ze'mir gegangen tsu a kozinke

00:26:27.460 --> 00:26:29.317
shlofn in a zayt gas,

00:26:29.345 --> 00:26:33.035
un un bay togs zenen mir gegangen aroyf oyf di, tsu di poyern,

00:26:33.294 --> 00:26:37.270
az me hot moyre gehat in a shtot, di doytshn veln arayn, UNK mit di bombes.

00:26:37.765 --> 00:26:39.076
eyn mol gey ikh

00:26:39.487 --> 00:26:40.527
in der fri

00:26:40.651 --> 00:26:44.662
hot men getrofn a poylish ⟨aza⟩ UNK CHokolad.

00:26:45.595 --> 00:26:49.491
zogt eyn polak tsu dem andern, ikh hob dir gezogt, ikh hob zey gehert adurkhgeyn, di shpyonen.

00:26:49.491 --> 00:26:51.609
ale fentster zenen geven farklept,

00:26:51.620 --> 00:26:53.217
se zol nisht zayn keyn ⟨NEWS⟩.

00:26:54.472 --> 00:26:55.765
se geven fintster.

00:26:55.872 --> 00:27:00.544
un un un me hot gerufn dem meyor fun shtot, er hot geheysn VUID,

00:27:00.564 --> 00:27:02.569
un khevre fun di POLICE,

00:27:02.572 --> 00:27:06.804
un me hot gezogt ale geyts avek, geyts avek. rirts nisht dos on, dos iz,

00:27:06.804 --> 00:27:07.876
un me hot geleygt,

00:27:07.876 --> 00:27:09.654
punkt azoy vi a poylish,

00:27:09.845 --> 00:27:13.656
rirts nisht on! un zey hobn genumen, di, dey khevre fun POLICE,

00:27:13.659 --> 00:27:14.750
a lopete,

00:27:14.874 --> 00:27:18.631
zey hobn es getrogn oyf di UNK fun feld un zey hobn es bagrobn.

00:27:19.261 --> 00:27:21.736
efsher a fir yor shpeter,

00:27:21.944 --> 00:27:24.048
undz hobn gehat a shokhnt antkegn,

00:27:24.222 --> 00:27:27.223
zi hot gehat a UNK fun CHokolads fun UNK,

00:27:27.260 --> 00:27:29.009
zi hot moyre gehat tsu voynen

00:27:29.572 --> 00:27:33.869
i- tsu shteyn bay ir hoyz, zi hot gehat a tokhter voynen bay zayt gas,

00:27:33.942 --> 00:27:36.800
hot zi genumen, se nisht geven keyn azlekhe gesheftn vi do,

00:27:36.800 --> 00:27:38.631
hot zi getrogn tsu di tokhter,

00:27:38.631 --> 00:27:40.619
zi hot undz dos fartseylt, zi hot moyre gehat,

00:27:40.760 --> 00:27:44.259
un zi hot zi hot farloyrn di CANDY, dos iz geven ir's,

00:27:44.259 --> 00:27:46.694
zi hot gevolt tsurikgeyn in kokh, hot er nisht gelozt

00:27:47.054 --> 00:27:51.793
un dos iz nisht geven keyn sam, dos iz geven, zi hot moyre gehat tsu redn, ven di doytshn gefinen oys dos

00:27:51.793 --> 00:27:53.799
shist men zi bald far azone zakhn.

00:27:54.209 --> 00:27:57.241
zi hot BUT undz hot zi fartseylt az dos iz geven ir CANDY.

00:27:58.630 --> 00:27:59.564
nakher

00:27:59.564 --> 00:28:01.038
di doytshn zenen arayn,

00:28:01.482 --> 00:28:03.049
azoy vi zenen arayn

00:28:03.085 --> 00:28:05.476
hobn zey bald aroysgehongnen di tsetlekh

00:28:05.549 --> 00:28:08.668
ales gegn yidn, vos me tor, vos me tor nisht.

00:28:08.668 --> 00:28:11.529
di yidn torn nisht aroysgeyn vayter vi do.

00:28:11.574 --> 00:28:13.537
di yidn

00:28:13.582 --> 00:28:17.739
farbotn a sakh zakhn. me tor nisht aroysgeyn

00:28:17.739 --> 00:28:19.839
far akht oder nayn in der fri,

00:28:19.839 --> 00:28:21.764
zekser muz men shoyn zayn tsurik.

00:28:21.764 --> 00:28:24.438
un bald tsugeshribn, ver se vet nisht dos folgn

00:28:24.438 --> 00:28:25.540
vert er geshosn.

00:28:26.120 --> 00:28:30.974
ikh gedenk eyn mol hobn zey getrofn eynem a yid, a UNK ⟨heyst er⟩, er hot gehat a froy mit a kind,

00:28:31.267 --> 00:28:35.027
un zey hobn im getrofn, er hot nisht ge⟨UNK⟩ aheymtsukumen far zeks,

00:28:35.030 --> 00:28:36.627
ken zayn efsher

00:28:36.920 --> 00:28:38.208
tsen nokh zeks,

00:28:38.208 --> 00:28:40.435
hot er geheysn kumen tsu zikh in di

00:28:40.435 --> 00:28:41.288
OFFICE,

00:28:41.288 --> 00:28:42.820
un er hot im geshosn far dem,

00:28:43.147 --> 00:28:44.980
gelozt a froy mit a kind.

00:28:44.851 --> 00:28:46.567
velkhn yor iz dos geven?

00:28:46.741 --> 00:28:50.836
dos hot gemuzt zayn in nayntsn fertsik azoy.

00:28:51.567 --> 00:28:53.435
ye bald, se bald aroys

00:28:54.875 --> 00:28:57.513
di ale zakhn, iz bald di ale gezetsn

00:28:57.513 --> 00:29:00.607
ales gegn yidn, gezetsn yidn kenen nisht geyn keyn SCHOOL,

00:29:00.916 --> 00:29:04.693
yidn torn nisht dos un ales gegn di yidn.

00:29:04.730 --> 00:29:05.740
gegn di yidn.

00:29:05.740 --> 00:29:08.212
un di nakher hot er aroysgegebn gezetsn

00:29:08.212 --> 00:29:09.719
ver se hot a gesheft

00:29:09.792 --> 00:29:11.815
fun shnits-skhoyre vi undz hobn gehat,

00:29:11.815 --> 00:29:12.807
shikh,

00:29:12.864 --> 00:29:14.697
zeyf, nokh azelkhe,

00:29:14.770 --> 00:29:17.127
hot men nisht getort farkoyfn. tsugemakht di gesheft.

00:29:17.184 --> 00:29:21.161
mir veln zikh do opshteln un aribergeyn tsum vayterdikn film.

00:29:18.550 --> 00:29:19.287
ye

00:29:21.099 --> 00:29:22.241
ye OKEY
